rmity,\n- Details on documentation required for compliance,\n- Administrative information for manufacturers and authorities.\n\n**If you need the word-for-word text of ANNEX VII:**\nThe only way to ensure precise legal accuracy is to download the regulation from the official EUR-Lex source and extract ANNEX VII from the official document【3:0†source】.\n\nLet me know if you need help interpreting or summarizing the legal text once you've accessed the annex from EUR-Lex!",
